          <p class='first-para'>
            I, too, have sympathy with the amendment. Can the Minister confirm that Clause 155, which provides that the provisions of the Bill shall,
            <q>come into force in accordance with provision made by order",</q>
            allows for different parts of the Bill to be brought into effect at different times?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0622P0-05695'>
        <a name='S5LV0622P0_20010301_GCR_118'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
