      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0622P0-05860'>
        <a name='S5LV0622P0_20010301_GCR_283'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-malcolm-sinclair' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010301_GCR_283' title='Link to this speech by Mr Malcolm Sinclair' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-malcolm-sinclair" title="Mr Malcolm Sinclair">The Earl of Caithness</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I am grateful to the Minister. With that, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-05861'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010301_GCR_284' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-05862'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010301_GCR_285' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
